{"tid":1709823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍田被鶳便衣狗(高清狗貌)，附加發夢過程","createTime":"2019-11-12T03:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T12:53:13.000Z","uid":165288,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ef7dc2274165d06112dc9e1b12524a9aa7234b","tid":1709823,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/heoj9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fheoj9&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=3ebcb7cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/heoj9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YCc7Vw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YCc7Vw.jpg&h=b683cb38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nESc7VD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnESc7VD.jpg&h=163959a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽人說，發夢經過係咁，強調以下只是虛構!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n[話佢影人起磚，之後手足就追佢，好多手足圍住佢已經再走唔到，起初大家都估唔到佢係狗，有人篤下佢腰間有沒有裝備，係乜都冇，加上個樣似係大陸哩藍絲等等。<br />\n佢個手機已一早比人搶咗，最終去咗邊就唔知，大家比足時間佢証明自己係咩身份，佢一言不答，之後手足就鶳，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但最重要嘅野冇做，冇人禁低佢唔比動，有人想取佢個袋之制，但佢已經開始逃脫走上消防車</span>]<br />\n<br />\n起底呢家野我(朋友嘅朋友嘅朋友)話唔識，我(朋友嘅朋友嘅朋友)話已經做盡，起碼影到佢相，眼見身旁冇人影佢相，係有個記者錄片。"},{"pid":"1cd39d5bc195f3386e802b34d807b1b520c63e35","tid":1709823,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"一D傷都無?"},{"pid":"fb90bd6a7bdfe2ebf3f9a902189c5ec93da4094f","tid":1709823,"uid":165288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1cd39d5bc195f3386e802b34d807b1b520c63e35","tid":1709823,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"一D傷都無?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"呢個係鶳前，鶳後爆晒剛，有人想爆佢菠蘿蓋，打唔正。<br />\n感覺上大家都未好確定佢係狗，如果唔係應該GG了"},{"pid":"28e3224cd60adcf6a3db9e20a73387989a8da53e","tid":1709823,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"大陸人樣，識唔識講廣東話架？"},{"pid":"8aca60d393ea98dfa65e045679f5f4899cd6429d","tid":1709823,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27c38dc1cd427378bc58b9cb6c43a3b61465293","tid":1709823,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28e3224cd60adcf6a3db9e20a73387989a8da53e","tid":1709823,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"大陸人樣，識唔識講廣東話架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"屌，你睇野可唔可以睇清少少，都話佢一言不答"},{"pid":"0fa7116ba96b9b17a0c64ba89447d22dfa6c8466","tid":1709823,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"睇片見佢有曱甴棍"},{"pid":"db62e36bb143a08eefd02636f592c65024c9e134","tid":1709823,"uid":165288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0fa7116ba96b9b17a0c64ba89447d22dfa6c8466","tid":1709823,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"睇片見佢有曱甴棍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"說漏了，這是佢搶咗手足支棍，絕對唔係佢本人，因為事後個手足高叫比佢搶咗，之後個個圍消防車，最終交回支棍。"},{"pid":"ec1eac1328d10ed7f5648b1d4bf8adca497dfce2","tid":1709823,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db62e36bb143a08eefd02636f592c65024c9e134","tid":1709823,"uid":165288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0fa7116ba96b9b17a0c64ba89447d22dfa6c8466","tid":1709823,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"睇片見佢有曱甴棍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"說漏了，這是佢搶咗手足支棍，絕對唔係佢本人，因為事後個手足高叫比佢搶咗，之後個個圍消防車，最終交回支棍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"仲有就係確認左啦<br />\n消記琴日自己出聲明話保護左個休班曱甴<br />\n<br />\n唔洗驚喎，打曱甴要繼續做"},{"pid":"12bba0ec8143ef10f6339d1bd4c03f5f105f7fa